📣 MASSIVE GIVEAWAY 📣 *GIVEAWAY CLOSED*
.
How’s ur skin condition lately? Has it been dry and rough to the touch, with some days looking dull and u don’t even feel u’re beautiful? If u hv, ur not alone. ‘Cos.. I feel the same way too... 🙆🏻‍♀️
.
As a skincare and beauty advocate, I’m ALWAYS on the lookout for great beauty and skincare products, so when I came across a new beauty oral supplement in the market which promises to give me clearer and brighter skin, I’m game for it! 🙋🏻‍♀️
.
After I’ve shared my thoughts on 𝗛𝗲𝗹𝗶𝗼𝗰𝗮𝗿𝗲 𝗣𝘂𝗿𝗲𝘄𝗵𝗶𝘁𝗲 𝗥𝗮𝗱𝗶𝗮𝗻𝗰𝗲 last week, many hv been asking whether they shld get it and try the oral supplements for themselves. 🙌🏻 I’m glad tt u guys trusted me w my reviews, so I’ve decided to do a MASSIVE GIVEAWAY for my followers who would like to try out @heliocaresg oral supplements. 🥰
.
For the giveaway, I’ll be giving away a specially bundled set worth $180 SGD for not 1, not 2, not 5 but 🔟 winners!!! Say what!!! 🤭😱🤩🤪 Open to all locals! Giveaway closes on 26th May 2359H.

What’s inside the bundled set ($180)?
- Heliocare Purewhite Radiance x 1
- Heliocare Advanced XF Gel SPF50 x 1
- $20 online store e-gift card
- FREE courier delivery to ur home during this #circuitbreakersg period

All u have to do to qualify as 1 of my 10 winners is:
✨ Follow me at @sherlenelian, @heliocaresg & @dermaskinshopsg
✨ Like my post
✨Comment w an emoji 😍 AND tag ur BFFs

That’s it!! How simple to be in the running for my giveaway! 🤩 Looking forward to bless u guys and let’s GLOW at home tgt! 💖
Take care of the skin during this circuit breaker @shennss @xjessxmex @jy1987
I’ll indicate all the 10 winners and DM each one individually tmr!! 🙌🏻😘

📣 Thanks guys for participating in this giveaway! 🙌🏻 Pls continue to stay well and beautiful in these uncertain times! 💜 Now, onto announcing the winners! In no particular order, the winners for this giveaway are @mabel_fang @xhazel_nutxx @keruri.kelly @perlie.mx @kensq @estraordinary_faith @fabbytoe @lidyatink @jorlynchew @yeetvonnee 🎉 U’ll receive a DM later in ur inbox! ✨🙏🏻
